social_posts.post_text: Two years since we said goodbye but here’s 15 minutes of you saying ‘Hello.’ Video edit by @squigenny - follow that page for lots of fun Lenny & Squiggy moments. Full videos on The Squigenny YouTubepage #davidlander #lennyandsquiggy

Happy Birthday Jared! There’s no one else I would eat outside with during torrential downpour, only to have the power go out, and then eat pizza on the floor of our hotel room. I love you ❤️ (oh and the cable was out).
Went on safari in my neighborhood. It’s a jungle out there! STAY SAFE FROM WILD GIRAFFES AND REINDEER!! (Disclaimer: I know my Australian accent needs work).

Had an amazing evening supporting @raise_up_ua! Congrats to @katya_suss for all of the hard work she has put in to help the people in Ukraine. Thank you @erosenfield for bringing me as your date! 💙💛 PS I’m still dreaming about that borscht.
I love a holiday where you celebrate by eating things fried in oil! Happy Hanukkah to all!! 🕎
This weekend we hugged all the chickens and kissed all the cows. All of them! Thank you @aynsstagram for taking me to @thegentlebarn - I can’t wait to go back. I miss Earl the Emu.
Merry Christmas from me and my dog from Rent-A-Dog-Photo! I now have my very own pet holiday photo thanks to Rent-A-Dog-Photo!
Me & My Maliboo 🌊🤍 (Yes, we bought matching shirts in Malibu. Yes, we pulled over on PCH to take this photo. Yes, we are adults).
Happy Birthday @ashleyargota9 can’t wait to celebrate you!! (And see the toilet 🚽 IYKYK)! 💜💜💜

Carole Cook was and will always be a legend! I feel so lucky to have had the chance to meet her an get to know her. She always had a story, a joke, or some deep wisdom to share with you. She was performing all the way to the end! She was a marvel! But I’m most grateful to have been witness to the beautiful bond between her and my dear friend @masonmcculley. Thank you Mason for sharing Carole with all of us. Our lives are better for it 💜
I’ve never met a penguin I didn’t like🐧
Happy Birthday to my Mom! @kathy_lander
Hope everyone had a romantic Valentine’s Day! Who was your special Valentine? 💗#valentine #grwm #comedy

social_posts.post_text: ‘Hot Girl Summer’ is OUT… ‘Hot Springs Summer…’ IN.
I saw the shrine…
They look sweet, but these guys will literally bite your ass for a cookie. I don’t blame them, I love cookies too.

Took some big steps on our trip to Japan. And tomorrow, we Take Steps (in Santa Monica) for the Crohn’s & Colitis Foundation! So proud of Jared and all he’s done to raise awareness over the past 9 years! Link in bio to donate!

Had the most amazing time staying at The Ugenta Sagenta, a two room Ryokan in Kibune Kyoto. The place was stunning and our personal concierge, Naomi, was the best! I wish I could have brought her back with me! I miss her 😭 Thank you to @tablethotels for helping us find this gem!

That’s a wrap on Japan (for now)! My biggest takeaways: People respect public spaces, toilets are ample and clean, everyone tries their best to help you, everything has a cute mascot, and 7-11’s are basically fine dining! Can’t say enough good things about our trip! Everyone should visit, it’s truly magical ✨

Had a lovely chat with @officialbroadwayworld about the world premiere of “Sukkot” at  @the6thact among other things 🍋 link in bio 🔗

Had an amazing time last night at @theartofelysium’s annual Heaven Gala. I started volunteering with them in 2010; thank you to @masonmcculley for introducing me to their workshops. Since then, I have been able to experience the amazing work that the Art of Elysium does first hand. Art truly does heal. Congrats to @jenniferkhowell and @lesannculp for all that you do! And thank you to @aphroditecamello for bringing me as your date! Please consider donating to Art of Elysium if you can!

Happy closing to the cast and crew of @scissorhandsmusical - I had the chance to breifly step in for the AMAZINGLY talented @aellis3 (please go to her page and watch her videos STAT). Very proud and grateful to have been a small piece of this beautiful puzzle created by @bradleybredeweg. Also, being a cover is not for the faint of heart. I have so much MORE respect for anyone who has ever done this. Thank you Alex for being so gracious and making be feel a part of this role. The bonus of this whole experience is gaining a new friendship in my adult life ❤️Thank you to the stunning cast @ryanoconnor1981 @carlyjcasey @jkaib @emmahunton @natalie.masini @carsonhiggins @johnakrause @dionnegipson who shoved with love and made me feel so supported. And to my fellow covers @theamandakruger & @ejboatzzz - we did it! Proud is an understatement. Also thank you to @thekelleyparker @itsjoshdamnit @chaddmcmillan @alyssaswann_ @saraannefahey for being so amazing and doing all that you do🤩 okay. Done gushing. Byyyyeeee!! Happy Closing!! It’s not the end, it’s the beginning ✂️🤚💚 photo by: @itsjoshdamnit
